reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 8, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Quality. Cute Color. Many size options.
reviews.reviewText: The pink is a soft dusty rose color. The bags have a soft, water repellant material and are very good quality. Zippers also zip smoothly. Bags are perfect for travel, hold a lot, and fit well in suitcase. Definitely worth purchasing, and Looking forward to buying more pieces from this particular line. 💕

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 18, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The quality of these is great! I like to wash my cubes after every couple of trips and these did great in the wash. I let the dry on low for just a few minutes and then air dry the rest of the way. I love that you can use them together or apart. And the size variety is great for me!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Serves its purpose
reviews.reviewText: I expected these to have more structure but they worked fine on a recent trip. Clothes were less wrinkled and definitely more organized. I don’t think I’ll ever use the hanging feature.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 14, 2022
reviews.reviewText: I was hesitant to purchase because there were not many reviews, but glad I did! The cubes are a great size and the three medium ones zip together easily. I used them the first time this past weekend and it was very convenient to take the cubes out of the suitcase and hang them in the closet. I have been looking for something like this for a while where you do not need a shelf/dresser to unpack. I am very happy with the purchase so far.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Flimsier than it seems
reviews.reviewText: The display pics and the emphasis on sturdiness make it seem like it holds its shape well and is made of a more rigid fabric. In reality when you actually put clothes in it, it gets shapeless, lumpy, and flimsy. These aren't trash-tier but they're not high quality either. Average for the price.
